title: Silver Top Laner Looking For Team
body: Keen to be apart of an actual team, I love the field of competitive play. League has now become my main game to play, and I'd love to have people to play with. (I'm 20, living in Perth). Still have a lot to learn in the game, but I learn very quickly. Recently high top lane win rate with Yasuo, I can also JG Master Yi, or ADC Ashe, i love them all.{{champion:157}} {{champion:11}} {{champion:22}}

replies.body:
Add me in game, I help run a discord community where I'm the coordinator for our ranked teams program. Hope to hear from you soon, I'm sure we have what you're looking for!

- Huskey (Ranked Team Coordinator for AGC)
Sure man, i added you, thats if your league name is just "Huskey". When you add me back, link me your discord :)
